# NocoDB Job Positions Integration Walkthrough

## Overview

I have successfully integrated the TD Games Career Portal with your self-hosted NocoDB instance to dynamically fetch job positions and display job descriptions.

## Changes Made

### New Files Created

#### [useJobs.ts](file:///e:/TDC_App/hiring_tdgames/src/hooks/useJobs.ts)
A React Query hook that fetches job data from NocoDB:
- Connects to `https://nocodb.tdconsulting.vn`
- Uses table ID `mh36y68rb3lserw` from base `pcrawiz8s9i03rk`
- Returns job titles (`job_tittle`) and descriptions (`description`)

#### [JobDescriptionPanel.tsx](file:///e:/TDC_App/hiring_tdgames/src/components/JobDescriptionPanel.tsx)
A new component that displays job description in a styled panel:
- Shows placeholder when no job is selected
- Displays job title and description with glassmorphism styling

